  <section style="padding: 3rem 1rem; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      Investment Opportunities
    </h1>

    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 2rem;">
      Welcome to the members-only investment page of <strong>AmicBridge</strong>.
      Here, paying members get access to verified insights into <strong>crypto assets</strong>,
      <strong>real estate</strong>, and <strong>emerging markets</strong>—all carefully analyzed
